                br
                p Where the Application provides such features, you may also report content, block other users, or mute notifications directly through the Application's interface. The Service Provider will review in-app reports with the same standards described in these Terms.
                br
                p The Service Provider may review reported content, request additional information where necessary, remove or restrict access to content, and take action against the responsible account where appropriate. Users affected by moderation decisions may contact the Service Provider at {{ appContact }} to request further review. The Service Provider will respond to appeals within a reasonable period and provide the reasons for any upheld moderation decision, subject to applicable law.
